NK013(pa)001:0: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po dpal sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba snying po bzhugs /
NK013(pa)001:2: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:3: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo /
NK013(pa)001:6: de bzhin gshegs pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das /
NK013(pa)001:8: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK013(pa)001:9: kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid
NK013(pa)001:10: / ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad dang /
NK013(pa)001:11: so so ma yin tha mi dad dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK013(pa)001:12: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa na /
NK013(pa)001:13: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba la /
NK013(pa)001:14: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK013(pa)001:15: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK013(pa)001:16: yon tan dpag tu med par rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK013(pa)001:17: lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa /
NK013(pa)001:18: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad /
NK013(pa)001:19: so so ma yin ngo bo nyid gcig pa'i ye shes kun tu 'khyil ba /
NK013(pa)001:20: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes rin po che'i dbyibs dang /
NK013(pa)001:21: kha dog la sogs pa rnam pa tha dad pa'i bye brag dang khyad par du gyur pa /
NK013(pa)001:24: ye shes rin po che sna tshogs kyi phreng ba dang /
NK013(pa)001:31: reg bya sna tshogs kyis phyogs bcur 'khrigs par rang byung la /
NK013(pa)001:32: mi sgrib par gsal ba'i rgyan bsam gyis mi khyab pas bklubs pa /
NK013(pa)001:33: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i sgo khyud can /
NK013(pa)001:34: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta babs dang ldan pa /
NK013(pa)001:35: phyi dang nang med pa kun tu yang nang du gyur pa na /
NK013(pa)001:36: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang /
NK013(pa)001:37: stobs glang po che'i khri dang /
NK013(pa)001:40: thogs pa med pa nam mkha' lding gi khri dang /
NK013(pa)001:41: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK013(pa)001:42: gos pa med pa pad+ma rin po che'i gdan la /
NK013(pa)001:43: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa /
NK013(pa)001:44: thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal zhing mtshan dang dpe byad dang ldan pa /
NK013(pa)001:45: bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du /
NK013(pa)001:46: sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba /
NK013(pa)001:47: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK013(pa)001:48: ye shes drug gi phyag ye shes rin po che'i phyag rgya 'bar ba can /
NK013(pa)001:49: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbu gsum dang ldan pa /
NK013(pa)001:50: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK013(pa)001:51: de bzhin gshegs pa gzugs kyi rgyal po dang /
NK013(pa)001:52: de bzhin gshegs pa tshor ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK013(pa)001:53: de bzhin gshegs pa 'du shes kyi rgyal po dang /
NK013(pa)001:54: de bzhin gshegs pa 'du byed kyi rgyal po dang /
NK013(pa)001:55: de dag kun kyang mthing ga dang /
NK013(pa)001:60: btsun mo dam pa snang ba'i dbyings dang /
NK013(pa)001:64: bskyod pa'i dbyings la sogs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang
NK013(pa)001:65: gnyis su med par chos kyi dbyings kun tu mtha'
NK013(pa)001:68: dper na til gyi gong bu bzhin du gang nas khyab par bzhugs so //
NK013(pa)001:69: de nas byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong ba dang /
NK013(pa)001:70: byang chub chen po rdo rje thos pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:71: byang chub chen po rdo rje snom pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:72: byang chub chen po rdo rje myong ba dang /
NK013(pa)001:73: btsun mo mthong bar bya ba dang /
NK013(pa)001:76: myong bar bya ba'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:77: byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong byed dang /
NK013(pa)001:78: byang chub chen po rdo rje thos byed dang /
NK013(pa)001:79: byang chub chen po rdo rje snom byed dang /
NK013(pa)001:80: byang chub chen po rdo rje myong byed dang /
NK013(pa)001:85: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg pa dang 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg byed dang /
NK013(pa)001:86: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg bya dang /
NK013(pa)001:87: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg shes dang /
NK013(pa)001:88: btsun mo rtag par ma yin pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:89: chad par ma yin pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:90: bdag tu ma yin pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:91: mtshan mar ma yin pa la sogs pa /
NK013(pa)001:92: de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK013(pa)001:93: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang
NK013(pa)001:94: gnyis su med pa'i gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor de dag
NK013(pa)001:95: nyid kyi gsang ba 'di nyid sku dang gsung dang
NK013(pa)001:96: thugs dang yon tan dang phrin las rdo rje las
NK013(pa)001:97: phyung ngo // e e ma e ma hoh de
NK013(pa)001:98: bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid dbang sgyur ye shes dkyil
NK013(pa)001:100: rang snang ba nyid ting 'dzin gzugs brnyan sgyu ma rnam dag gsal ba ni /
NK013(pa)001:101: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las sel med pa yi yon tan yid bzhin rin po che /
NK013(pa)001:102: mi zad par ldan rgyan gyi 'khor lo rdo rje mchog gi gnas nyid do //
NK013(pa)001:103: zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK013(pa)001:104: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las gleng gzhi'i le'u ste dang po'o //
NK013(pa)001:106: // de nas bcom ldan 'das byed pa po rdo rje yid kun tu bzang po /
NK013(pa)001:107: thams cad ma lus pa'i rang bzhin gyi tshul rdo rjes /
NK013(pa)001:108: btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun tu bzang mo la 'jug par gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:109: zhugs pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK013(pa)001:110: ma lus pa thams cad gcig gi rang bzhin dbyer
NK013(pa)001:111: med pas de bzhin gsheg pa nyid /
NK013(pa)001:112: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:113: e ma hoh rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK013(pa)001:114: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK013(pa)001:115: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun //
NK013(pa)001:116: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK013(pa)001:117: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai //
NK013(pa)001:118: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK013(pa)001:119: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK013(pa)001:120: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK013(pa)001:121: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK013(pa)001:122: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK013(pa)001:123: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos //
NK013(pa)001:124: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi brnyes so //
NK013(pa)001:126: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:127: de nas btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun tu bzang mo /
NK013(pa)001:128: bcom ldan 'das yid kun tu bzang po dang gnyis su med par gyur nas /
NK013(pa)001:129: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:130: kye ma'o phyogs bcu stong khams ye nas dben //
NK013(pa)001:131: srid pa gsum nyid dag pa'i zhing //
NK013(pa)001:132: snyigs ma lnga nyid bde ldan gnas //
NK013(pa)001:133: phung po lnga nyid rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK013(pa)001:134: thams cad mchog gi snying po las //
NK013(pa)001:135: gzhan du rgyal bas chos mi btsal //
NK013(pa)001:136: nyid las gzhan zhes bya ba'i chos //
NK013(pa)001:137: btsal kyang rgyal bas mi brnyes so //
NK013(pa)001:139: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis mkhyen to //
NK013(pa)001:140: de nas gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid chen pos
NK013(pa)001:141: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i sems ye shes su bskyed
NK013(pa)001:143: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos /
NK013(pa)001:144: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK013(pa)001:145: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK013(pa)001:146: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK013(pa)001:147: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)001:148: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK013(pa)001:152: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)001:153: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK013(pa)001:154: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK013(pa)001:155: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK013(pa)001:156: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)001:157: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK013(pa)001:158: dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK013(pa)001:159: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK013(pa)001:160: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)001:161: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK013(pa)001:167: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang btsun mo'i tshogs thams cad kyang mnyes pas khyab par gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:168: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang /
NK013(pa)001:169: btsun mo'i tshogs thams cad dang bcas pas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:170: e ma ho ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK013(pa)001:171: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK013(pa)001:172: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK013(pa)001:173: gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK013(pa)001:175: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang /
NK013(pa)001:176: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo
NK013(pa)001:177: nyid du gcig pa'i mtshan nyid yin pas dbyer med
NK013(pa)001:178: na'ang / 'gro ba'i rnam par rtog pa ma rig pa las /
NK013(pa)001:179: 'gro ba lnga'i ris bsam gyis mi khyab par smin pa la /
NK013(pa)001:180: thugs rje chen po sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen po skyes nas /
NK013(pa)001:181: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:182: e ma ho bde gshegs snying po las //
NK013(pa)001:183: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK013(pa)001:184: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK013(pa)001:185: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK013(pa)001:186: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK013(pa)001:187: sus kyang ma bcings bcings med de //
NK013(pa)001:188: bcing bar bya ba yod ma yin //
NK013(pa)001:189: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yis //
NK013(pa)001:190: nan gyis mkha' la mdud pa 'dor //
NK013(pa)001:191: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:192: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK013(pa)001:193: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK013(pa)001:194: ces de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched du gleng ngo //
NK013(pa)001:195: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:196: las don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyi byang chub
NK013(pa)001:197: sems ye shes su bskyed pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o
NK013(pa)001:199: // // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las /
NK013(pa)001:200: thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis brlabs zhes bya ba'i /
NK013(pa)001:201: rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug /
NK013(pa)001:202: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'thon to /
NK013(pa)001:204: / 'thon nas kyang las kyi dbang gis s+n+rel gzhi dang
NK013(pa)001:205: yan man gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha'
NK013(pa)001:206: yas mu med pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po
NK013(pa)001:207: re rer / thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das
NK013(pa)001:208: re res 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis 'gro ba lnga'i
NK013(pa)001:209: re rer / don mdzad de / bltams pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:214: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK013(pa)001:215: cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:216: mya ngan las 'das pa la sogs par ston pa'i thub pas /
NK013(pa)001:217: dus gzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:218: thams cad kyi sems kyi rgyud kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:219: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyan gyis thams cad kun tu gzigs pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:220: rdzu 'phrul gyi snyan gyis kun tu gsan pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:221: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho gas kun tu don spyod pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:222: zag pa med pa kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa
NK013(pa)001:223: rdzogs pa'i mngon par shes pa chen po drug dang
NK013(pa)001:224: / kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:225: kun tu thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:226: kun tu zhal bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:227: kun tu gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa /
NK013(pa)001:228: bsam gyis mi khyab pa grangs med pa phyogs bcur snang bar gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:230: 'dul ba'i dbang gis lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:231: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:232: rang byang chub kyi theg pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:233: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:234: bla na med pa'i theg pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:235: ma rig pa'i rnam par rtog pa nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gnyen por /
NK013(pa)001:236: chos stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi gsungs so //
NK013(pa)001:239: de dag thams cad kyang gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i
NK013(pa)001:240: phyi nang gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba 'dzin
NK013(pa)001:242: las dang las kyi 'bras bu chud mi za ba dang /
NK013(pa)001:243: las dang las kyi 'bras bus mi gos /
NK013(pa)001:245: gos su med par ston pa'i mthar thug go //
NK013(pa)001:246: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:248: ma rig rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK013(pa)001:250: mi mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:251: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK013(pa)001:252: yang dag sgyu ma'i tshul gnyis su //
NK013(pa)001:253: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan med de //
NK013(pa)001:254: rnam dag dbyings nyid tshul gcig go //
NK013(pa)001:255: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan rnams ni //
NK013(pa)001:256: log par rtog pa tsam nyid las //
NK013(pa)001:257: phra zhing zab pa'ang yod ma yin //
NK013(pa)001:258: log rtog nyid la nyid spyod pas //
NK013(pa)001:259: gzhan du g.yo ba ci yang med //
NK013(pa)001:260: log rtog rgyu 'bras rgyun nyid kyang //
NK013(pa)001:261: gzhi rtsa med dbyings skad cig ma //
NK013(pa)001:262: rnam par dag pa'i dbyings nyid tshul //
NK013(pa)001:263: nyid la dbang sgyur nyid spyod phyir //
NK013(pa)001:264: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK013(pa)001:265: rnam dag bla med theg pa'i mchog /
NK013(pa)001:266: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK013(pa)001:267: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK013(pa)001:268: yang dag rtogs pas rab brtags na //
NK013(pa)001:269: rang bzhin med las cir yang 'grub //
NK013(pa)001:270: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' /
NK013(pa)001:272: / chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK013(pa)001:273: ma rig smin mdzad 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK013(pa)001:274: byung nas mya ngan 'da' bar ston /
NK013(pa)001:276: / 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK013(pa)001:277: dam tshig sgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:278: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK013(pa)001:279: phyogs bcu kun tu rab grags pa //
NK013(pa)001:280: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK013(pa)001:281: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK013(pa)001:282: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi /
NK013(pa)001:285: chos rnams ming du btags pa tsam //
NK013(pa)001:286: ston pas don dang mthun phyogs su //
NK013(pa)001:287: ming dang tshig tu btags nas bstan //
NK013(pa)001:288: ston ming tshig la dngos po med //
NK013(pa)001:290: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa gnyis su med pa'i
NK013(pa)001:291: dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyis gsang ba 'di nyid
NK013(pa)001:292: / sku dang gsung dang thugs yon tan phrin las rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK013(pa)001:293: a hoh srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs bdag tu rtog las 'phros //
NK013(pa)001:294: rgyud drug skye 'gag lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK013(pa)001:295: gnas dang sdug bsngal 'khrul 'khor la sogs pa //
NK013(pa)001:296: log rtog nyid las gzhan du ci yang med //
NK013(pa)001:297: stong nyid bdag med ye mkhyen rang rig thugs //
NK013(pa)001:298: dmigs bya dmigs byed med par dran dbang sgyur //
NK013(pa)001:299: ngo mtshar sku gsung yon tan zhing khams las //
NK013(pa)001:300: gzhan na med de de nyid de ltar yin //
NK013(pa)001:301: zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK013(pa)001:303: thub pa drug gi sprul pa grangs med pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:304: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsungs pa yang
NK013(pa)001:305: de dag tu 'dus par de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK013(pa)001:306: kyis mkhyen to // gsang ba'i snying po de kho
NK013(pa)001:307: na nyid nges pa las chos thams cad gtan la
NK013(pa)001:308: phab pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:310: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dgongs pa gcig tu gyur nas /
NK013(pa)001:311: mnyam pa chen po'i tshul rdo rje'i dbyings su /
NK013(pa)001:312: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ting nge 'dzin las mi g.yo bar /
NK013(pa)001:313: chos thams cad ming tsam du gnas pa'i yi ge phreng ba'i 'khor lo zhes bya ba 'di /
NK013(pa)001:314: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK013(pa)001:315: ah rab tu brtan gyur a dkar las /
NK013(pa)001:316: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams spro //
NK013(pa)001:317: phyogs bcu gang bar gsal gyur nas //
NK013(pa)001:319: de las ming tshogs gsal 'bar kun //
NK013(pa)001:320: spro zhing bsdu ba'ang de bzhin no /
NK013(pa)001:322: / 'di ni rdo rje dngos grub kyi //
NK013(pa)001:323: brtan byung ye shes rgyu yin no //
NK013(pa)001:324: ah ka kha ga g+ha nga /
NK013(pa)001:336: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa /
NK013(pa)001:340: chos thams cad ming gi mtshan nyid tsam du gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:341: hoh de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:342: a ni stong dang mi stong gi //
NK013(pa)001:343: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK013(pa)001:344: thams cad ming tsam sangs rgyas kun //
NK013(pa)001:345: yi ge phreng ba nyid la gnas //
NK013(pa)001:346: a nyid sna tshogs par snang ba'i //
NK013(pa)001:347: ka la sogs pa bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK013(pa)001:348: sgra yi ming gis thams cad bsdus //
NK013(pa)001:349: mngon rdzogs rgyal por de nyid nges //
NK013(pa)001:350: e ma ho ngo mtshar ya mtshan gyi /
NK013(pa)001:352: / 'phrul chen bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i ming //
NK013(pa)001:353: tshig rnams ma lus 'dzin pa'i gnas //
NK013(pa)001:354: sna tshogs don chen smra zhing ston //
NK013(pa)001:355: dngos med yi ge'i rang bzhin sems //
NK013(pa)001:356: bdag med mtha' bral mi dmigs kyang //
NK013(pa)001:357: dbyibs dang kha dog ming tshogs kyi //
NK013(pa)001:358: rol pa cir yang sprul cing ston //
NK013(pa)001:359: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:360: ye shes sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)001:361: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga nyid //
NK013(pa)001:362: yi ge mgo nas k+sha la rdzogs //
NK013(pa)001:363: sems kyi rang bzhin yi ge ste //
NK013(pa)001:364: yi ge dngos po yod ma yin //
NK013(pa)001:365: dmigs med de nyid sna tshogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:366: sku gsung thugs kyi 'khor lo che //
NK013(pa)001:367: sku gsung thugs ni ngo mtshar gyi //
NK013(pa)001:369: dbyings la dbyings kyis bris pa ste //
NK013(pa)001:370: yi ge zhes ni de phyir brjod //
NK013(pa)001:371: mgo ni ma nor lam yin te //
NK013(pa)001:372: tig ni shes rab ming du smra //
NK013(pa)001:373: shad ni thabs chen tshigs su gcod //
NK013(pa)001:374: a ni skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK013(pa)001:375: tha ni sgyu 'phrul rdo rje nyid //
NK013(pa)001:376: ta ni snang ba'i sgyu 'phrul nyid //
NK013(pa)001:377: da ni sgyu 'phrul yid bzhin nyid //
NK013(pa)001:378: d+ha ni sgyu 'phrul rnam dag nyid //
NK013(pa)001:379: na ni kun tu sgyu 'phrul nyid //
NK013(pa)001:380: tha ni d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs nyid //
NK013(pa)001:381: ta ni d+r+wa bas brtan pa nyid //
NK013(pa)001:382: da ni d+r+wa bas lham me nyid //
NK013(pa)001:383: d+ha ni d+r+wa bas 'khril ba nyid //
NK013(pa)001:384: na ni d+r+wa bas kun tu 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:385: ka ni spyan gyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:386: kha ni snyan gyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:387: ga ni shangs kyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:388: g+ha ni ljags kyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:389: nga ni thugs kyang 'jig byed pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:390: tsa ni spyan gyi sku yi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:391: tsha ni snyan gyi sku yi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:392: dza ni shangs kyi sku yi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:393: dz+ha ni ljags kyi sku yi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:394: nya ni sku yang 'jig byed pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:395: pa ni spyan gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:396: pha ni snyan gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:397: ba ni shangs kyi gsung gi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:398: b+ha ni ljags kyi gsung gi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:399: ma ni gsung yang 'jig par byed //
NK013(pa)001:400: ya ni skye ba rnam par dag /
NK013(pa)001:401: wa ni gnas pa dag pa yin //
NK013(pa)001:402: ra ni 'jig pa dag pa ste //
NK013(pa)001:403: la ni stong pa dag pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:404: sha ni rtag pa dag pa ste //
NK013(pa)001:405: sha ni chad pa'ang yod ma yin //
NK013(pa)001:406: sa ni mtha' bral bdag med pa //
NK013(pa)001:407: ha ni mtshan ma med pa nyid //
NK013(pa)001:408: k+sha ni ye shes thugs kyi thugs //
NK013(pa)001:409: i ni rdul snyed lha rnams su /
NK013(pa)001:411: / +ai ni rdul snyed lha ma yin //
NK013(pa)001:412: u ni rdul snyed mi rnams su /
NK013(pa)001:414: / +au ni rdul snyed byol song rnams //
NK013(pa)001:415: e ni rdul snyed yi dwags su //
NK013(pa)001:416: ee ni rdul snyed dmyal ba rnams //
NK013(pa)001:417: o ni thams cad 'jig par byed //
NK013(pa)001:418: oo ni thams cad zhig pa yin //
NK013(pa)001:420: sku gsung thugs kyi phreng ba bsdus //
NK013(pa)001:422: a hoh de nas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i
NK013(pa)001:423: tshogs dang gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag
NK013(pa)001:425: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK013(pa)001:426: a hoh thabs dang shes rab dgyes sprin byang chub sems tshogs rgyu 'khor lo /
NK013(pa)001:428: / 'bras bu rgyal ba smin grub ngo mtshar ming tshogs bzhi bcu gnyis /
NK013(pa)001:430: / 'dus ma byas nyid 'dus byas rdo rje dkyil 'khor 'byin pa'i dam /
NK013(pa)001:432: / 'da' bar mi mdzad dbang med rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pa'i mthu chen yin //
NK013(pa)001:433: a hoh rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK013(pa)001:435: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad yi ge'i 'khor lor gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:436: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:437: las yi ge phreng ba'i 'khor lo bkod pa'i le'u
NK013(pa)001:439: de nas yi ge 'khor lo'i sprin bkod pa las
NK013(pa)001:440: sgyu 'phrul rnam par 'phro ba 'di ched du brjod
NK013(pa)001:441: do // rtsa ba med pa'i semasasa nyid ni //
NK013(pa)001:442: chos rnams kun kyi rtsa ba yin //
NK013(pa)001:443: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK013(pa)001:444: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK013(pa)001:446: d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pas //
NK013(pa)001:447: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:450: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel cing //
NK013(pa)001:451: longs spyod 'byung zhing ngan song sbyong //
NK013(pa)001:453: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung zhing /
NK013(pa)001:459: thams cad stongs shing ltung bar 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:460: dgug dang btang dang bcing dang dgrol //
NK013(pa)001:461: gso dang bsad dang 'pham dang rgyal //
NK013(pa)001:463: de nyid ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK013(pa)001:464: ming tshig gzugs sogs yid bzhin gyis //
NK013(pa)001:465: mun la snang byung ji bzhin du /
NK013(pa)001:468: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal //
NK013(pa)001:469: dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya rnams //
NK013(pa)001:470: ma nyams shes shing yo byad ldan /
NK013(pa)001:473: dus gsum rgyal bas thugs chud pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:474: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ni //
NK013(pa)001:475: zad pa'i dus med yid bzhin mdzod /
NK013(pa)001:478: dngos po med las dngos po'i sprin //
NK013(pa)001:480: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med par //
NK013(pa)001:481: rtogs pa'i dbang sgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK013(pa)001:482: gang gis dmigs med mi shes pa //
NK013(pa)001:483: de yis chos kyi dbyings mi shes //
NK013(pa)001:484: de phyir dngos dang dngos med pa /
NK013(pa)001:486: / 'jig pas dmigs med shes par gyis //
NK013(pa)001:487: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK013(pa)001:488: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK013(pa)001:489: mtshan med ma yin rigs brgyud min //
NK013(pa)001:490: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK013(pa)001:491: gnas su ma yin gang yang min //
NK013(pa)001:492: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK013(pa)001:493: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK013(pa)001:494: thabs las thabs byung thabs bsam yas //
NK013(pa)001:495: tha dad min las tha dad pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:496: nang dang nang gi phyi rol gyi //
NK013(pa)001:497: dkyil 'khor bsam yas ye shes rol /
NK013(pa)001:499: / 'jigs med kun bzang phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK013(pa)001:500: gang gis glang chen myos 'dra'i sems //
NK013(pa)001:501: mnyam par bzhag pas btul nas su //
NK013(pa)001:502: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK013(pa)001:503: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:504: zhes brjod pas de bzhin gshegs pa nyid gzigs mos mnyes par gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:505: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:506: las sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bsgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK013(pa)001:509: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang
NK013(pa)001:510: bzhin gcig dang du ma med pa'i bdag nyid thams
NK013(pa)001:511: cad kyis / 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad la /
NK013(pa)001:512: nyid kyi che ba'i dkyil 'khor dbyung bar bzhed nas /
NK013(pa)001:513: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:514: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK013(pa)001:515: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub ni //
NK013(pa)001:516: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK013(pa)001:519: / 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NK013(pa)001:520: gru chad bzhis brgyan bar khyams dang //
NK013(pa)001:521: kun tu gru bzhi sgo khyud ldan //
NK013(pa)001:522: rol mo sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin //
NK013(pa)001:523: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK013(pa)001:524: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung //
NK013(pa)001:525: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK013(pa)001:526: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK013(pa)001:527: gdan la rdzogs dang sems dpa'i tshul /
NK013(pa)001:529: / 'khor lo rgyal po rgyal mo dang //
NK013(pa)001:530: g.yas nas mthong thos snom pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:531: myong dang btsun mo'i tshogs su bcas //
NK013(pa)001:532: gru chad la ni mthong byed dang //
NK013(pa)001:533: thos byed snom byed myong byed rnams //
NK013(pa)001:534: btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas par gnas //
NK013(pa)001:535: bar khyams la ni thub drug dang //
NK013(pa)001:536: mdun dang rgyab tu byed pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:537: bya ba dag ni gnas par bstan //
NK013(pa)001:538: sgo khyud bzhi la 'joms pa ni //
NK013(pa)001:539: btsun mo'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas //
NK013(pa)001:540: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK013(pa)001:542: ut+pala klu shing la sogs mtshan //
NK013(pa)001:543: mdzes tshul mnyes pa'i yo byad 'dzin //
NK013(pa)001:544: mthing ga dkar po ser le brgan //
NK013(pa)001:545: ljang gu la sogs sna tshogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:546: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK013(pa)001:547: gsal 'tsher lhun sdug gzi byin ldan /
NK013(pa)001:552: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:553: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)001:554: sku yi phyag rgya che mchog ni //
NK013(pa)001:555: de bzhin dbyings las ma g.yos kyang //
NK013(pa)001:556: yang dag thar pa'i gzugs sku dang /
NK013(pa)001:559: mthun byas sku ni sna tshogs ston //
NK013(pa)001:560: ston nyid sgyu ma mig yor tshul //
NK013(pa)001:561: tshul nyid dbyings las g.yos pa med //
NK013(pa)001:562: ma g.yos bzhin du sna tshogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:563: de'i tshe mi mthun sna tshogs la //
NK013(pa)001:564: so so 'dra bar snang ba ni //
NK013(pa)001:565: de bzhin nyid kyis ma bcos kyang //
NK013(pa)001:566: las 'phro'i dbang gis so sor snang //
NK013(pa)001:567: dper na me long chu zla bzhin //
NK013(pa)001:568: de tshe 'gro drug thams cad la //
NK013(pa)001:569: sdig spong gzugs su snang bar bstan //
NK013(pa)001:570: nyan thos rnams la dgra bcom gzugs //
NK013(pa)001:571: rang rgyal rnams la bse ru'i tshul //
NK013(pa)001:572: gzhan yang theg mchog rim pa bzhin /
NK013(pa)001:574: / 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK013(pa)001:575: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK013(pa)001:576: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK013(pa)001:577: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK013(pa)001:578: sku yis chos rnams mjal bar ston //
NK013(pa)001:579: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK013(pa)001:580: dngos kyi mdog ngan thams cad sel /
NK013(pa)001:582: / 'khor gyis de bzhin sku bltas na //
NK013(pa)001:583: byang chub sgrib pa gting dpag med //
NK013(pa)001:584: me long bzhin du sku la snang //
NK013(pa)001:585: de nas sa bcu rim gyis 'byang //
NK013(pa)001:586: bla med byang chub yang dag thob //
NK013(pa)001:587: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK013(pa)001:588: longs sku zad med yid bzhin gter //
NK013(pa)001:589: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK013(pa)001:590: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK013(pa)001:591: spyod yul kun tu man+da la //
NK013(pa)001:592: tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs par rol //
NK013(pa)001:593: thabs dang shes rab sa yi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:594: de la sogs pa bsam yas mchog /
NK013(pa)001:595: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung sku //
NK013(pa)001:596: nyon mongs kun gyi zhing du gnas //
NK013(pa)001:597: zad mi shes pa'i gter du 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:598: rdo rje rig pa 'dzin pa'i sku //
NK013(pa)001:599: thams cad dbyer med mnyam pa'i sku //
NK013(pa)001:600: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes sku //
NK013(pa)001:601: de tshe sku lnga kun kyang rdzogs //
NK013(pa)001:603: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med
NK013(pa)001:604: pa thams cad du dkyil 'khor brjod kyis mi lang
NK013(pa)001:605: ba / zhing gi rdul snyed du gsal bar gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:606: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang
NK013(pa)001:607: gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi
NK013(pa)001:608: gsang ba 'di nyid sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK013(pa)001:609: las rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK013(pa)001:610: a hoh dmigs bya dmigs byed mi dmigs dpag med bsam mi khyab /
NK013(pa)001:611: ye shes rang rig dkyil 'khor sna tshogs brjod mi lang //
NK013(pa)001:612: mnyam dang mi mnyam kun khyab khyab med khyab pa'i dbyings //
NK013(pa)001:613: ye nas kun gsal dkyil 'khor rnam spros spros pa med //
NK013(pa)001:614: hoh zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK013(pa)001:615: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las dkyil 'khor spros pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:617: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang
NK013(pa)001:618: bcas pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs
NK013(pa)001:619: rdo rje las 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK013(pa)001:620: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shwa d+d+he /
NK013(pa)001:631: k+sh+aim hi r+aa dza yah tram +aa gar+b+ha yah hri
NK013(pa)001:632: ha h+aum pad+ma pa da mah dzim ku ru p+aa
NK013(pa)001:633: na h+r+aih h+aum l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wamh t+r+aam
NK013(pa)001:634: m+aa l+ye sa ma ya hoh h+r+ai g+ai ti r+aa
NK013(pa)001:635: ko&a ham / a n+ri ti r+aa ga y+aa mi /
NK013(pa)001:636: mee d+h+aa ra ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)001:637: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)001:638: h+aum sa r+aa dza ya swa h+aa /
NK013(pa)001:639: mum sh+r+ai am r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)001:642: bam d+ai pa su khi n+ai /
NK013(pa)001:648: ma h+aa badz+ra 5d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:649: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:650: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:651: ma h+aa karma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:653: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta ah mu ne krem s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)001:654: mu ne h+aum t+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)001:659: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan /
NK013(pa)001:660: ma h+aa k+aa ru ni k+aa dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)001:661: dzahh+aum bam hoh +aa h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)001:668: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)001:669: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK013(pa)001:670: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)001:671: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK013(pa)001:674: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh dzah h+aum bam hoh zhes brjod pas /
NK013(pa)001:677: / 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad khyab par grags so //
NK013(pa)001:680: de nas bcom ldan 'das byed pa po rdo rje dang /
NK013(pa)001:681: bya ba mo rdo rje gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor la thim par mdzad do //
NK013(pa)001:682: de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK013(pa)001:683: bdag nyid chen pos bdag nyid chen po'i ye shes
NK013(pa)001:684: dang byin bsdu ba zhes bya ba 'di sku dang
NK013(pa)001:685: gsung dang thugs rdo rje sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las
NK013(pa)001:686: phyung ngo // ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)001:687: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma 1ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)001:688: ma h+aa prat+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba +aat+ma 3ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)001:689: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma 2ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)001:690: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+th+aa na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma 4ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)001:691: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)001:692: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aa t+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)001:693: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko & ham /
NK013(pa)001:694: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa
NK013(pa)001:695: ga na badz+ra wa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko & ham
NK013(pa)001:696: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)001:698: thim par gyur gsal bar gyur 'bar bar gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:699: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)001:700: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung //
NK013(pa)001:701: sgra dang ming tshig kun las 'das //
NK013(pa)001:702: sna tshogs sgra rnams gsal bar 'byung //
NK013(pa)001:703: gsung gcig dkyil 'khor yan lag ni //
NK013(pa)001:704: bsam gyis mi khyab kun tu khyab //
NK013(pa)001:705: sgra dang ming tshig so sor grags //
NK013(pa)001:706: thams cad gsung gi phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK013(pa)001:707: rgyud mchog sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK013(pa)001:708: bde ldan gsung gi don 'byung ba'ang //
NK013(pa)001:709: thams cad pad+ma'i ngang gyur na //
NK013(pa)001:710: grol thar lam dang 'khor ba'i sgra //
NK013(pa)001:711: ji skad brjod kyang gsung mchog ste //
NK013(pa)001:712: theg pa mtho dman thams cad dang //
NK013(pa)001:713: log 'gro ma lus thams cad skad //
NK013(pa)001:714: byang chub rdo rje'i gsung du bsdus //
NK013(pa)001:715: bsdus nyid phyogs bcur rnam par grags //
NK013(pa)001:716: sgra nyid ma chags ngang du gsungs //
NK013(pa)001:717: gsungs pa nyid na brjod du med //
NK013(pa)001:718: brjod med de nyid sna tshogs sgra //
NK013(pa)001:719: kun la grags shing so sor mjal //
NK013(pa)001:720: dper na de bzhin sbrid sangs bzhin //
NK013(pa)001:721: gsung gcig sgra yis so sor go //
NK013(pa)001:722: de ni gsung mchog rgyal po yin //
NK013(pa)001:723: theg pa mtho dman bsam yas kyang //
NK013(pa)001:724: de bzhin nyid las ma gsungs te //
NK013(pa)001:725: gdung bya'i thabs su so sor thos //
NK013(pa)001:726: ji ltar gsung rab kun brjod kyang //
NK013(pa)001:727: de bzhin nyid kyis gsungs pa med //
NK013(pa)001:728: yi ge med dang rig pa'i gsung //
NK013(pa)001:729: ljags kyi rtse mor ma phyung yang //
NK013(pa)001:730: thugs rje gsung gi byin rlabs kyis /
NK013(pa)001:732: / 'gro don sna tshogs so sor gsal //
NK013(pa)001:733: gsal nyid gsung gi rdo rje'i mchog /
NK013(pa)001:734: de bzhin gsung gi 'gro don rnams //
NK013(pa)001:735: de bzhin ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK013(pa)001:736: dper na brag ca'i sgra bzhin no //
NK013(pa)001:737: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:738: las dkyil 'khor 'dus pa dang gsang sngags kyi le'u
NK013(pa)001:740: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK013(pa)001:741: yan lag thams cad dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub
NK013(pa)001:742: par byin gyis rlob pa zhes bya ba 'di ched
NK013(pa)001:743: du brjod do // sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bas mngon rdzogs pa //
NK013(pa)001:744: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK013(pa)001:745: gsang ba de nyid nges pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:747: mi bskyod nyi ma'i dkyil yi ge //
NK013(pa)001:748: rin chen zla ba'i dkyil yi ge //
NK013(pa)001:749: lnga gnyis zung du sprad pa las //
NK013(pa)001:750: sbyar bas phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK013(pa)001:751: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te /
NK013(pa)001:753: / 'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad pa //
NK013(pa)001:754: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK013(pa)001:755: bde ba chen po sbyin pa'i rgya /
NK013(pa)001:757: / 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)001:758: h+aum sgreng rtse mor rdo rje 'bar //
NK013(pa)001:759: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril gsil zhing /
NK013(pa)001:761: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten /
NK013(pa)001:763: / 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)001:764: m+aum sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)001:766: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta /
NK013(pa)001:768: / 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)001:770: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril gsil zhing /
NK013(pa)001:772: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten /
NK013(pa)001:774: / 'bru bzhi spas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)001:775: l+aam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)001:777: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta /
NK013(pa)001:779: / 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)001:780: s+w+aam sgreng rtse mor rin chen 'bar //
NK013(pa)001:781: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril gsil zhing /
NK013(pa)001:783: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten /
NK013(pa)001:785: / 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)001:786: m+aam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)001:788: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta /
NK013(pa)001:790: / 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan /
NK013(pa)001:793: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril gsil zhing /
NK013(pa)001:795: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten /
NK013(pa)001:797: / 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)001:798: p+y+aam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)001:800: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta /
NK013(pa)001:802: / 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)001:803: h+aam sgreng rtse mor ral gri 'bar //
NK013(pa)001:804: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril gsil zhing /
NK013(pa)001:806: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten /
NK013(pa)001:808: / 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)001:809: t+aam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)001:811: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK013(pa)001:812: ut+pala klu shing la sogs mtshan //
NK013(pa)001:813: rin chen myu gu ral gri 'bar //
NK013(pa)001:815: chos kyi 'khor lo rin cen snye //
NK013(pa)001:816: gzugs mdzes rin cen phreng ba dang //
NK013(pa)001:817: pi wang gar mkhan mchog nyid de //
NK013(pa)001:818: me tog phreng dang spos mchod ma //
NK013(pa)001:819: mar me byug pa la sogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:820: las la 'khril zhing chos la brten //
NK013(pa)001:822: gong gi phyag rgya chen po bzhin //
NK013(pa)001:823: gnyis med dbyings kyi ngang du 'khril //
NK013(pa)001:824: sgo bzhi'i khro bo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK013(pa)001:825: n+ri mgo gdengs dang rdo rje gnon //
NK013(pa)001:826: thod sprul chen po gnon pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:827: rdo rje rgya gram las kyis gnon //
NK013(pa)001:828: lcags kyu zhags pa s+pho ta hoh sgo bzhir gnas pa de dag kyang /
NK013(pa)001:831: thub drug phyag rgya sna tshogs te //
NK013(pa)001:832: mdor bsdus phyag rgya drug yin no //
NK013(pa)001:833: yum ni dmigs med chos kyi dbyings //
NK013(pa)001:834: kun bzang mnyam gzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK013(pa)001:836: gzhan yang phyag rgya sna tshogs te //
NK013(pa)001:837: yang na de bzhin gshegs nyid dam //
NK013(pa)001:838: yang na rdo rje thal mo nyid //
NK013(pa)001:839: phyag rgya chen po'i tshogs mchog ni //
NK013(pa)001:840: thabs dang shes rab ldan 'byor na //
NK013(pa)001:841: ma bskyod ma bsgul thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)001:842: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK013(pa)001:843: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK013(pa)001:844: de nyid yan lag spros bdag ste //
NK013(pa)001:846: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gis //
NK013(pa)001:847: rgyal ba rgyal mchog de bzhin du //
NK013(pa)001:849: de la sogs te bsam mi khyab //
NK013(pa)001:850: phyogs bcu dus bzhi bsam yas su /
NK013(pa)001:852: / 'dul ba'i don rnams so sor ston //
NK013(pa)001:853: theg pa mtho dman thams cad dang //
NK013(pa)001:854: phyin ci log rnams bsam yas dang //
NK013(pa)001:855: zhi khro'i tshogs chen thams cad la //
NK013(pa)001:856: so sor mthun byas kun tu snang //
NK013(pa)001:857: dper na gar mkhan nyid 'dra ba //
NK013(pa)001:858: lus la ma bkod sna tshogs ston //
NK013(pa)001:859: mdor na phyag rgya thams cad ni /
NK013(pa)001:861: / 'di zhes gcig ces brjod du med //
NK013(pa)001:862: gnyis dang gsum du rnam par 'phro //
NK013(pa)001:863: bskyod dang spro ba'ang de bzhin te //
NK013(pa)001:864: mdor na bsgul bskyod thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)001:865: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK013(pa)001:866: gnas nyid mi gnas gnas pa'ang min //
NK013(pa)001:867: de skad dag mchog nyid kyis bshad //
NK013(pa)001:868: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:869: las yan lag thams cad dkyil 'khor du byin gyis
NK013(pa)001:870: brlabs nas phyag rgya spros pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o
NK013(pa)001:872: // // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen pos /
NK013(pa)001:873: rdo rje gsang ba'i dam tshig bkod pa la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK013(pa)001:874: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:875: shin tu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK013(pa)001:876: phyag rgya chen po'i phyag mthil du //
NK013(pa)001:877: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa de //
NK013(pa)001:878: sor ni bzhi yi tshad du bya /
NK013(pa)001:880: / 'bru lnga spos lnga rin cen lnga //
NK013(pa)001:881: snying po lnga dang sman lnga dang //
NK013(pa)001:882: bdud rtsi lnga nyid rab mnyam la //
NK013(pa)001:883: rig pas thig ni gdab par bya //
NK013(pa)001:884: lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:885: rtsibs bzhi 'khor lo mu khyud bcas //
NK013(pa)001:886: gru cad bzhi dang gru bzhi pa //
NK013(pa)001:887: bar khyams sgo khyud ldan par bya //
NK013(pa)001:888: sen zlum tsam gyi nyi zla la //
NK013(pa)001:890: yungs 'bru tsam gyi yi ge las //
NK013(pa)001:891: phyag rgya til 'bru tsam du bri //
NK013(pa)001:892: bcos bu'i ras ni sna tshogs dang //
NK013(pa)001:893: rgyan phreng btung dang bro bas bskor //
NK013(pa)001:894: glu tshig bro gar rol mo yi //
NK013(pa)001:895: sprin phung tshogs kyis rab tu mchod //
NK013(pa)001:896: yum dang 'jo ma sems ma yis //
NK013(pa)001:897: ji ltar 'dod pa'i las bzhin mchod //
NK013(pa)001:898: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan par //
NK013(pa)001:899: zhal du gyur pa'i me bos la //
NK013(pa)001:900: bza' btung bro ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK013(pa)001:901: las bzhi'i mchod pa rab tu sbyin //
NK013(pa)001:902: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de bzhin te //
NK013(pa)001:903: shin tu phra la sbyangs pa yis //
NK013(pa)001:904: bsam yas dag la'ang de bzhin bya //
NK013(pa)001:905: rig pas dpag pa tsam du'o //
NK013(pa)001:906: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK013(pa)001:907: sems kyi yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK013(pa)001:908: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK013(pa)001:909: mnyen 'jam reg na bde ba yi //
NK013(pa)001:910: sna tshogs rin po che yi gzhi //
NK013(pa)001:911: mdzes par bris shing spras pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:913: dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog bsil //
NK013(pa)001:914: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK013(pa)001:915: rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal //
NK013(pa)001:916: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK013(pa)001:917: bla bre rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK013(pa)001:918: do shal dpung rgyan se mo do //
NK013(pa)001:919: bza' dang btung ba'i mchog rnams dang //
NK013(pa)001:920: rang la mdzes par brgyan pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:921: lha dang lha mo rdul snyed kyis //
NK013(pa)001:922: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK013(pa)001:923: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK013(pa)001:924: dkyil 'khor kun la rgyas par dbul //
NK013(pa)001:925: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK013(pa)001:926: rim gyis yang na cig car du //
NK013(pa)001:927: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK013(pa)001:928: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:929: gsal ldan ma'am byin brlabs la //
NK013(pa)001:930: stong gsum yungs 'brur gzhug tshul du //
NK013(pa)001:931: dbyings nas dkyil 'khor spyan drangs mchod //
NK013(pa)001:932: mnyes nas grub pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK013(pa)001:933: bdag nyid chen po mchod pa yis //
NK013(pa)001:934: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus mnyes //
NK013(pa)001:935: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad la //
NK013(pa)001:936: dga' ba chen pos khyab par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:937: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba brtan pa yis //
NK013(pa)001:938: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:939: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus dang //
NK013(pa)001:941: lus ngag sems dang chos thams cad //
NK013(pa)001:942: gang na'ang mi gnas mi dmigs pa //
NK013(pa)001:943: mig yor tshul du sbyor ba yis //
NK013(pa)001:944: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:945: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK013(pa)001:946: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK013(pa)001:947: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK013(pa)001:948: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK013(pa)001:949: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK013(pa)001:950: rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK013(pa)001:951: dbang phyug longs spyod lngas mchod na //
NK013(pa)001:952: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin //
NK013(pa)001:953: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor smos ci dgos //
NK013(pa)001:954: nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:955: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK013(pa)001:956: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK013(pa)001:957: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK013(pa)001:958: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzung //
NK013(pa)001:959: yang na thal mo rab bsnol nas //
NK013(pa)001:960: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang du ni //
NK013(pa)001:961: dkyil 'khor mdzub gang tshad du yang //
NK013(pa)001:962: mkhas pas cho ga ji bzhin bya //
NK013(pa)001:963: yang na sa gzhi rab mnyam la //
NK013(pa)001:964: dkyil 'khor khru gang tshad du bya //
NK013(pa)001:965: yang na lus gang tshad du ste //
NK013(pa)001:966: yang na lus ni gsum gyi tshad //
NK013(pa)001:967: phur bu srad bu tshon phye dang //
NK013(pa)001:968: gos rgyan mdzes pa'i yid 'ong grogs //
NK013(pa)001:969: thig gdab cho ga phun sum tshogs //
NK013(pa)001:970: mkhas ldan chen pos bsgrims te bya //
NK013(pa)001:971: yang na khru ni bcu drug dang //
NK013(pa)001:972: nyi shu'am nyi shu rtsa lngar bya //
NK013(pa)001:973: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor lnga rnams bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:974: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang dgod //
NK013(pa)001:975: yang na rgyang grags dpag tshad dam //
NK013(pa)001:976: nam mkha'i dbyings ni bsam yas par //
NK013(pa)001:977: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor sna tshogs bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:978: ma mthong rmongs la bstan phyir tshon //
NK013(pa)001:979: kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga'am //
NK013(pa)001:980: lnga yi tshon gyi bri bar bya /
NK013(pa)001:982: / 'dul ba'i cho ga bzhin du dgye //
NK013(pa)001:983: ting 'dzin rol mo mtha' yas mchog /
NK013(pa)001:984: yi ge'am gdan nam snying po'am //
NK013(pa)001:985: phyag rgya'am sku gsung thugs ldan par //
NK013(pa)001:986: byin rlabs ya mtshan rmad po che /
NK013(pa)001:989: sa la sogs las phyag rgyar byas //
NK013(pa)001:990: rnam grol rim pa thob par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:991: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs pas //
NK013(pa)001:992: smos ci dgos te de nyid yin //
NK013(pa)001:993: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK013(pa)001:994: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK013(pa)001:995: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK013(pa)001:996: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la /
NK013(pa)001:998: / 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)001:999: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:1000: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK013(pa)001:1001: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1002: dpag bsam shing dang yid bzhin gyi //
NK013(pa)001:1003: rin po che dang 'byung ba kun //
NK013(pa)001:1004: de dag rdzas yod ma yin te //
NK013(pa)001:1005: rang sems bsod nams brtan pa yin //
NK013(pa)001:1006: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)001:1007: gzhan na yod 'ongs ma yin te //
NK013(pa)001:1008: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK013(pa)001:1009: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK013(pa)001:1010: shes rab dbyings kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK013(pa)001:1011: thabs kyi phyag rgyar gyur pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)001:1012: ye shes la ni ye shes rol //
NK013(pa)001:1013: ye shes rol pa nyid kyang gsog /
NK013(pa)001:1014: rgyal ba sngon byung skyob pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:1015: byin rlabs ston pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK013(pa)001:1016: bya byed nus pa'i gzi byin gyis //
NK013(pa)001:1017: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po'i mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1018: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing //
NK013(pa)001:1019: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK013(pa)001:1020: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pas //
NK013(pa)001:1021: ma nyams 'jug la rab brtson na //
NK013(pa)001:1022: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK013(pa)001:1023: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK013(pa)001:1024: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK013(pa)001:1025: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK013(pa)001:1026: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni //
NK013(pa)001:1027: ye shes thig le de nyid la //
NK013(pa)001:1028: ye shes thig le nyid snang ba //
NK013(pa)001:1029: bsam gyis mi khyab mtha' yas mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1030: phyogs bcu dus bzhi mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:1031: zhing khams rnam dag bsam yas dang //
NK013(pa)001:1032: rgya dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK013(pa)001:1034: / 'khor lo'i rgyan dang rol mo'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)001:1035: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsam yas kun //
NK013(pa)001:1036: mthong nas nye bar brnyes pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:1037: rgya chen gsung la don byung ba'ang //
NK013(pa)001:1038: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK013(pa)001:1039: gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK013(pa)001:1040: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK013(pa)001:1041: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te //
NK013(pa)001:1042: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK013(pa)001:1043: log par rtog brtags rnam dag cing //
NK013(pa)001:1044: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK013(pa)001:1045: thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na /
NK013(pa)001:1047: / 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK013(pa)001:1048: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)001:1049: stangs dpyal gnyis sam yang na lnga //
NK013(pa)001:1050: byas te bde ldan rab zhugs na /
NK013(pa)001:1053: skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes de //
NK013(pa)001:1054: gnyer na nye bar 'byung ba yi //
NK013(pa)001:1055: ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges //
NK013(pa)001:1056: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:1058: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:1059: las rdo rje bkod pa'i gsang ba'i dam tshig gi
NK013(pa)001:1062: // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po rgyal
NK013(pa)001:1063: po sbyin pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK013(pa)001:1064: snyoms par zhugs nas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod
NK013(pa)001:1065: do // shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK013(pa)001:1066: bde ba'i 'bru tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun //
NK013(pa)001:1068: rtse nas bstim zhing dkyil 'khor bsgyur //
NK013(pa)001:1069: nyan byed 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK013(pa)001:1070: gsal ba'i thig le ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)001:1071: t+r+aam gi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las //
NK013(pa)001:1072: rin chen dkyil 'khor gsal spro thim //
NK013(pa)001:1074: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gang //
NK013(pa)001:1075: gsang ba kun la'ang mnyan par bya //
NK013(pa)001:1076: gsang ba'i don nyid brtag pa las //
NK013(pa)001:1077: gzhan du smra bar bya ba min //
NK013(pa)001:1078: gsal ba'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK013(pa)001:1079: gsal ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)001:1080: yi ge phreng ba'i tshogs mchog las //
NK013(pa)001:1083: // dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po //
NK013(pa)001:1084: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gzung //
NK013(pa)001:1085: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mchod la //
NK013(pa)001:1086: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK013(pa)001:1087: lag pa'i 'khor lo'i gzhan yas su //
NK013(pa)001:1088: gsal ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)001:1089: h+aam gi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las //
NK013(pa)001:1092: // khyod ni rdo rje las yin gyis //
NK013(pa)001:1093: las rnams ma lus kun gyis shig /
NK013(pa)001:1095: khyod kyi dgos pa byed pa yin //
NK013(pa)001:1096: smra byed 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK013(pa)001:1097: gsal ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)001:1098: h+r+aihyiga phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las //
NK013(pa)001:1099: chos kyi 'khor lo gsal spro thim //
NK013(pa)001:1100: choos kyi bdud rtsi bla med kyis //
NK013(pa)001:1101: dad ldan skyes bu ngoms par byos //
NK013(pa)001:1102: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la //
NK013(pa)001:1103: mthun par gsang bsgrags gzhan du min //
NK013(pa)001:1104: bskyod chen 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK013(pa)001:1105: gsal ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)001:1107: dkyil 'khor lnga dang khro phreng bsgom /
NK013(pa)001:1109: // phyogs bcu dus bzhi thams cad kyi //
NK013(pa)001:1110: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK013(pa)001:1111: dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa po //
NK013(pa)001:1112: dkyil 'khor kun gyi sbyin pa spyod //
NK013(pa)001:1113: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK013(pa)001:1114: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK013(pa)001:1115: nyan pa la sogs rtsom pa rnams /
NK013(pa)001:1118: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK013(pa)001:1119: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK013(pa)001:1120: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK013(pa)001:1121: snying po lnga yis dbang bskur na //
NK013(pa)001:1122: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK013(pa)001:1123: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:1124: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK013(pa)001:1125: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:1127: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las dbang sbyin pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:1129: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen po
NK013(pa)001:1130: sgyu 'phyul d+r+wa ba'i rgyal po bsgyur ba zhes bya
NK013(pa)001:1131: ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK013(pa)001:1132: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:1133: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK013(pa)001:1134: byin gyis brlabs dang mngon sum par //
NK013(pa)001:1135: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK013(pa)001:1136: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK013(pa)001:1137: yan lag dbang po rnam shes kun //
NK013(pa)001:1138: rnam smin du shes par bya //
NK013(pa)001:1139: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1140: yang na khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1141: gzugs sgra dri ro reg la sogs //
NK013(pa)001:1142: rnam smin m+aum du shes par bya //
NK013(pa)001:1143: yum gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1144: yang na khro mo'i dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1145: gos rgyan bza' btung glu dang tshig /
NK013(pa)001:1146: bro gar tshogs kyi sprin phung la //
NK013(pa)001:1147: h+aum du shes pas rab spyad na //
NK013(pa)001:1149: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK013(pa)001:1150: dabye'am yang na mi dbye bar //
NK013(pa)001:1151: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK013(pa)001:1152: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po //
NK013(pa)001:1154: bde ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor spro //
NK013(pa)001:1155: sangs rgyas sprin tshogs ma lus la //
NK013(pa)001:1156: dgyes mnyam mchog gi sbyin pas bstim //
NK013(pa)001:1157: bsgrubs pa'i nyi zla'i snying po de //
NK013(pa)001:1158: dkyil 'khor rdo rje lce yis blang //
NK013(pa)001:1160: yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:1161: zhing gyur mchog dang mchog phran rnams //
NK013(pa)001:1162: nyi zla'i steng du mkhas pas bzhag /
NK013(pa)001:1163: nga rgyal lag gi 'du byed bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1164: h+aum du gyur pas rnam par dag /
NK013(pa)001:1165: dbyings su thim nas phyag rgya 'bar //
NK013(pa)001:1167: gtsug tu rnam par rgyal ba bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1168: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar pa'i thabs //
NK013(pa)001:1169: ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK013(pa)001:1170: sgyu mar snang ba mig yor tshul //
NK013(pa)001:1171: sbyor sgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK013(pa)001:1172: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med //
NK013(pa)001:1173: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK013(pa)001:1174: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK013(pa)001:1175: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK013(pa)001:1176: byed spyod tshogs chen gnyis gyur nas //
NK013(pa)001:1177: yan lag ma nyams yo byad ldan //
NK013(pa)001:1178: cho ga rdzogs par shes pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:1180: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK013(pa)001:1181: lnga dang lnga yi sbyor ba yi //
NK013(pa)001:1182: tshom bu lnga yi lha bkod la //
NK013(pa)001:1183: khro bo bcu dang khro mo bcu /
NK013(pa)001:1185: / 'khor lo'i tshul du rnam par bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1186: de bzhin rigs dang rdo rje'i rigs //
NK013(pa)001:1187: pad+ma'i rigs te sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)001:1188: khro bo tshogs dang ldan pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:1189: tshom bu gsum gyi lha rnams bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1190: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK013(pa)001:1191: thugs kyi thugs te thugs kyi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1192: khro bo tshogs dang ldan pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:1193: tshom bu gcig pa'i lha rnams bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1194: khro bo khro mo'i tshogs chen pa //
NK013(pa)001:1195: pho nya phyag brnyan bka' nyan tshogs //
NK013(pa)001:1196: ci bgyi la sogs tshogs rnams kyis //
NK013(pa)001:1197: dngos grub las rnams rdzogs par byed //
NK013(pa)001:1199: mnyam rdzogs lhun grub ngang gnas shing //
NK013(pa)001:1200: spyod pas ci la'ang thogs med pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:1201: thams cad ye nas dbyer med pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:1202: rdo rje'i rigs su thams cad dkyil /
NK013(pa)001:1205: chags med tshul gyis bstim par bya //
NK013(pa)001:1206: gnyis med gyur nas phyag rgya che //
NK013(pa)001:1207: yang na sku gsung thugs nyid de //
NK013(pa)001:1208: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)001:1210: gnyis med dbyings kyi ngang du thim /
NK013(pa)001:1213: nyon mongs sdug bsngal sel bar byed //
NK013(pa)001:1214: rdo rje'i rigs su skye ba'i gnas //
NK013(pa)001:1215: sngags 'chang dngos grub yang dag ni //
NK013(pa)001:1216: thabs dang shes rab thams cad kyis //
NK013(pa)001:1217: dkyil 'khor lnga dang khro phreng bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1218: chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis ni /
NK013(pa)001:1221: gnyis su med par bstim par bya //
NK013(pa)001:1222: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'grub //
NK013(pa)001:1223: rnal 'byor thabs dang shes rab kyis //
NK013(pa)001:1224: de bzhin gshegs dang yum du bsgoms //
NK013(pa)001:1225: sems dpa' sems ma nyid du bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1226: so so'i sngags dang phyag rgya dang //
NK013(pa)001:1227: ting 'dzin yang dag so sor gsal //
NK013(pa)001:1228: gnas dang longs spyod ci bde dang //
NK013(pa)001:1229: ma nyams blo ni rab ldan pas //
NK013(pa)001:1230: dang por dam nos bzhin du bya //
NK013(pa)001:1231: le lo sgyid snyoms med pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:1232: the tshom med par bsgrubs byas na //
NK013(pa)001:1234: rdo rje gsang mchog dam pa 'thob //
NK013(pa)001:1235: sgrub pa'i zhag dang tshes grangs ni //
NK013(pa)001:1236: rgyud las smos pa bzhin du bshad //
NK013(pa)001:1237: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK013(pa)001:1238: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la de bzhin gshegs pa nyid ched du gleng ngo //
NK013(pa)001:1239: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:1240: las tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi le'u ste bcu gcig
NK013(pa)001:1242: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen po rol mo'i sprin rnam par spros te /
NK013(pa)001:1243: rgyan bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:1244: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bas mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:1249: glu tshig sgra yi phyag rgya yis //
NK013(pa)001:1250: chos kyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:1251: rgyan dang bgo ba'i phyag rgya yis /
NK013(pa)001:1254: bza' dang btung ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NK013(pa)001:1255: yid bzhin sku dang bdud rtsi 'grub /
NK013(pa)001:1257: / +aa li k+aa li'i phyag rgya yis //
NK013(pa)001:1261: / 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK013(pa)001:1262: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK013(pa)001:1263: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK013(pa)001:1264: mi dang lha dang tshangs pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:1265: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK013(pa)001:1266: khyad par sa la gnas 'gyur yin //
NK013(pa)001:1267: pha rol phyin pa kun tu rdzogs //
NK013(pa)001:1268: thabs dang shes rab thabs kyi mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1269: shes rab mchog gi mchog gyur pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:1270: sa yi khyad par bcu dang gsum //
NK013(pa)001:1271: rgyu 'bras khyad par lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK013(pa)001:1272: mkha' dkyil dwangs pa'i dbyings nyi zla //
NK013(pa)001:1273: ye shes rgyal po stangs dpyal bsgom //
NK013(pa)001:1274: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)001:1275: ma lus par ni bsgom par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:1276: dus bzhi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK013(pa)001:1277: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:1278: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK013(pa)001:1279: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma tshol cig /
NK013(pa)001:1280: dkyil 'khor kun tu rab sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)001:1282: cho ga lhag gam ma tshang na //
NK013(pa)001:1283: skyon nyid dag ste nyes pa med //
NK013(pa)001:1284: ces ched du brjod pas rol mo'i sprin gyis mnyes par gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:1285: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las tshogs bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:1287: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK013(pa)001:1288: sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor thams
NK013(pa)001:1289: cad gcig tu bsdus nas dgyes pa chen pos /
NK013(pa)001:1290: chos thams cad ye nas rdzogs pa chen por lhun
NK013(pa)001:1291: gyis grub pa'i dam tshig shin tu gsang ba'i snying
NK013(pa)001:1292: po sprin bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK013(pa)001:1293: zhugs nas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:1294: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK013(pa)001:1295: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs /
NK013(pa)001:1297: / 'dul ba dgongs pa gsang ba dang //
NK013(pa)001:1298: rang bzhin gsang ba'i don rnams ni //
NK013(pa)001:1299: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK013(pa)001:1300: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK013(pa)001:1301: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK013(pa)001:1302: ston pa rdo rje'i thugs la gnas //
NK013(pa)001:1307: gsang ba'i thig le dkyil 'khor dbyings /
NK013(pa)001:1309: / 'byung ba shes rab rigs kyi yum //
NK013(pa)001:1310: chen po rigs kyi de bzhin te //
NK013(pa)001:1311: byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)001:1312: dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams //
NK013(pa)001:1313: kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)001:1314: bdag nyid chen po lhag pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:1315: thugs kyi ye shes lngas blta zhing //
NK013(pa)001:1316: snying po thig le mnyam sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)001:1317: bde ba'i ye shes rol mo yis //
NK013(pa)001:1318: ye shes dgyes la mchod pa 'bul //
NK013(pa)001:1319: zag pa med pa'i bsod nams kyis //
NK013(pa)001:1320: ye shes sgyu mar rang snang ba //
NK013(pa)001:1321: rol mo'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1322: gsang ba'i thig le nyid kyi dbyings //
NK013(pa)001:1323: de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK013(pa)001:1324: phyogs bcu dus bzhir mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:1325: sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs //
NK013(pa)001:1326: ma lus bdag nyid zhal mthong ba //
NK013(pa)001:1327: dbang sgyur mchog nyid dam pa yin //
NK013(pa)001:1329: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)001:1330: rgyan du dkyil 'khor ma lus thogs //
NK013(pa)001:1331: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor mnyam sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)001:1334: sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor sgrol ba yis //
NK013(pa)001:1335: bya byed med par dkyil 'khor spyod //
NK013(pa)001:1336: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)001:1337: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK013(pa)001:1338: rang byung kun dam lhun gyis grub /
NK013(pa)001:1340: / 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyis /
NK013(pa)001:1342: / 'da' bar mi mdzad dam tshig mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1343: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK013(pa)001:1344: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK013(pa)001:1345: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad du //
NK013(pa)001:1346: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:1347: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:1348: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK013(pa)001:1349: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas shing //
NK013(pa)001:1350: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi /
NK013(pa)001:1354: / 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na /
NK013(pa)001:1356: / 'das dang da ltar byung ba yi //
NK013(pa)001:1357: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK013(pa)001:1358: bsnyen nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs /
NK013(pa)001:1364: / 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi /
NK013(pa)001:1366: / 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK013(pa)001:1367: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la /
NK013(pa)001:1369: / 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK013(pa)001:1370: btsal kyang rgyal bas mi brnyes so //
NK013(pa)001:1371: kun gyi phyag rgya chen po'i mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1372: thos bsam bsgom la rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:1373: shes rab mig ldan rnams kyis zung //
NK013(pa)001:1374: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la brtan //
NK013(pa)001:1375: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK013(pa)001:1376: gzhan du nam yang sbyin mi bya //
NK013(pa)001:1377: rmongs la 'phyar bas gal te sbyin //
NK013(pa)001:1378: dus min par ni srog zad nas //
NK013(pa)001:1379: bsreg dang sbrebs la yun ring gnas //
NK013(pa)001:1380: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched du brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:1381: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:1382: las shin tu gsang ba man ngag gi snying po'i
NK013(pa)001:1385: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad nyid kyi
NK013(pa)001:1386: dkyil 'khor la dgyes pa chen po'i glu 'di blangs
NK013(pa)001:1387: so // phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:1388: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK013(pa)001:1389: bsod nams dkyil 'khor sku yi tshogs //
NK013(pa)001:1390: snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs hoh rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK013(pa)001:1391: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK013(pa)001:1392: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK013(pa)001:1393: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che hoh sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK013(pa)001:1394: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK013(pa)001:1395: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang /
NK013(pa)001:1397: / 'dus pa'i tshogs chen thig le che hoh mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK013(pa)001:1398: mtha' yas kun nas sna tshogs spro //
NK013(pa)001:1399: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK013(pa)001:1400: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po hoh phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK013(pa)001:1401: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK013(pa)001:1402: sprul pa'i rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK013(pa)001:1403: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub hoh thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)001:1404: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK013(pa)001:1405: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK013(pa)001:1406: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che hoh zhes bsgrags so //
NK013(pa)001:1407: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:1408: las mnyes pa'i mchod pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o
NK013(pa)001:1410: // // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag
NK013(pa)001:1411: po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid kyis
NK013(pa)001:1412: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor mngon par 'du mdzad de /
NK013(pa)001:1414: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:1415: brtags pa la mngon par zhen pas /
NK013(pa)001:1416: yang dag pa'i lam dang bral ba dag /
NK013(pa)001:1417: gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs pa sbas pa'i gsang ba la mngon par 'chel nas /
NK013(pa)001:1418: rgyu dang 'bras bu la rmongs pas /
NK013(pa)001:1419: srid pa'i sa bon rtsub mos 'phangs nas /
NK013(pa)001:1420: mtshams med pa'i rab tu tsha ba'i dmyal bar skyes so //
NK013(pa)001:1421: de rab tu tsha ba'i sdug bsngal drag pos gdungs pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:1422: 'di bas shin tu grang yang ci ma rung snyam pa'i mod la /
NK013(pa)001:1424: pad+ma ltar gas pa'i sdug bsngal drag po dag gis
NK013(pa)001:1425: rab tu gdungs pa de lta bu'i sdug bsngal rab
NK013(pa)001:1426: tu tsha ba la sogs pa brgyad dang /
NK013(pa)001:1427: shin tu grang ba la sogs pa brgyad po dag tu /
NK013(pa)001:1428: 'jig rten gyi khams brgyud cing bskal pa chen po stong phrag bcu gnyis su myong ngo //
NK013(pa)001:1429: de nas rnam par smin pa de zad pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:1431: skom pa'i sdug bsngal gyis rab tu nyen pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:1432: 'dod pa'i dngos po rnams yid du mi 'ong ba dang /
NK013(pa)001:1433: gdug cing rtsub pa'i dngos po sna tshogs su gyur pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:1435: shin tu rid cing bskams pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:1436: lus dang yan lag dang dbang po mi 'tshams par
NK013(pa)001:1437: gyur par bskal pa chen po drug tu skyes so
NK013(pa)001:1438: // de nas las kyi sgrib pa rtsub mo'i rnam par smin pa de khad kyis bsrabs pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:1439: sngon gyi srid pas mtshams sbyar nas /
NK013(pa)001:1440: yi dwags srin po chen po rab tu gdug pa
NK013(pa)001:1441: gtub po lus gcig la mgo bo brgya pa dang
NK013(pa)001:1443: lus brgya la mgo bo gcig pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:1446: yan lag sna tshogs pa dang /
NK013(pa)001:1447: gdug pa'i lag cha sna tshogs pa thogs pa /
NK013(pa)001:1450: 'jigs pa'i sgra sna tshogs sgrogs pa /
NK013(pa)001:1452: dri dang kha rlangs kyis thams cad skyi bung zhes byed pa /
NK013(pa)001:1453: rab tu 'jigs pa'i rlung nag dang /
NK013(pa)001:1455: tsha ba'i dbugs kyis phyogs ba cu kun tu khams 'khrug par byed pa /
NK013(pa)001:1456: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi 'debs par byed pa /
NK013(pa)001:1457: myos shing nyams par byed pa'i mthus /
NK013(pa)001:1459: lha ma yin gyi ris dang lha'i ris dang /
NK013(pa)001:1463: 'bras bu che ba man chad dbang du bsdus so //
NK013(pa)001:1464: de sngon bsten pa'i stobs kyis thams cad mkhyen pas gzigs nas thugs rjes 'dul bar gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:1465: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa che ba'i rdo rje bkod pa'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bas /
NK013(pa)001:1466: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu srid pa gsum gyi
NK013(pa)001:1467: bdag po 'dul ba'i nga rgyal chen po'i gzi brjid
NK013(pa)001:1468: ston pa'i phyir / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag po /
NK013(pa)001:1469: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos khro bo'i rgyal
NK013(pa)001:1470: po'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin chen po rnam par 'phro
NK013(pa)001:1471: ba'i / sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyal po'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NK013(pa)001:1472: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid nas /
NK013(pa)001:1473: khro mo dbang phyug chen mo mngon du phyung ste /
NK013(pa)001:1474: hi hi zhes dgyes pa'i gzi mdangs kyis /
NK013(pa)001:1475: rin cen pad+ma rgyas par mdzad nas /
NK013(pa)001:1476: gnyis su med par 'khril ba'i dgyes pas thim nas /
NK013(pa)001:1477: byang chub sems kyi sprin las /
NK013(pa)001:1478: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la
NK013(pa)001:1479: man+da la phata phata phata ha la ha la ha
NK013(pa)001:1481: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa khyab
NK013(pa)001:1482: par khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs stong gsum gyi
NK013(pa)001:1483: 'jig rten tsam / phyogs bcu'i rdul phra mo snyed 'thon par gyur nas /
NK013(pa)001:1484: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad g.yos /
NK013(pa)001:1501: / 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i stong khams thams cad na gnas pa'i dbang che ba dang /
NK013(pa)001:1503: mthu che ba'i dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa thams cad brgyal /
NK013(pa)001:1505: kun tu brgyal bar gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:1506: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po nyid /
NK013(pa)001:1507: 'jigs byed chen po shin tu rngam pa skyi bung
NK013(pa)001:1508: zhes byed pa'i 'bar ba chen po'i khrag 'thung sku
NK013(pa)001:1509: smug nag cir yang 'gyur ba dbu dang phyag dang
NK013(pa)001:1510: zhabs stong khams kyi rdul snyed mtshon cha sna tshogs
NK013(pa)001:1511: 'dzin pa de dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir gyur
NK013(pa)001:1512: te / dur khrod chen por dgyes nas khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil na /
NK013(pa)001:1513: keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi steng 'bar ba
NK013(pa)001:1514: chen po'i klong gi 'khor lo'i dkyil na dbang phyug
NK013(pa)001:1515: chen po dang / dur khrod kyi bdag po dregs
NK013(pa)001:1516: pa chen po khyo shug gi gdan la brkyangs bskums
NK013(pa)001:1517: chen po dang / su bzhugs so // khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin phung de dag kyang /
NK013(pa)001:1518: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen por gyur te shar phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK013(pa)001:1519: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po rin po cher gyur te lho phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK013(pa)001:1520: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po pad+mara gyur te nub phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK013(pa)001:1521: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po kun tu las su gyur te byang phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK013(pa)001:1522: de dag kun kyang 'jigs byed chen po'i cha lugs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1525: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis /
NK013(pa)001:1529: gshin rje la sogs pa khyo shug gis gdan byas pa la brkyangs bskums su bzhugs so //
NK013(pa)001:1530: btsun mo khrag 'thung chen mo'i tshogs rnams kyang so so'i sku la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs so //
NK013(pa)001:1531: rigs rigs lnga'i zhes pa nas ngo mtshar te zhes pa'i bar 'di rgya 'grel spar khab /
NK013(pa)001:1532: lnga'i he ru ka gcig tu bstims te bsdus nas /
NK013(pa)001:1533: gcig gis mang po 'dul ba'i ngo mtshar te /
NK013(pa)001:1534: de nas dregs pa chen po la sogs pa gtum pa'i sems kyis gdug pa'i rdzu 'phrul rong zom /
NK013(pa)001:1536: g.yung ston pa'i 'grel pa bzhir mi gsal zhing /
NK013(pa)001:1537: rgya dper yang mthong ba ma byung mod /
NK013(pa)001:1538: sgrol t+aika tu snang bas rgya dpe mi mthun pa gcig gnyis shig byung ngam snyam /
NK013(pa)001:1540: de nas dbang phyug chen po brtse ba can dregs pa chen po zhes bsnon ma yang 'dug go //
NK013(pa)001:1541: chen po sna tshogs bstan nas /
NK013(pa)001:1542: mgrin gcig tu gdug pa'i nga ros /
NK013(pa)001:1543: barlanga po'i gtum tshig tu smras pa /
NK013(pa)001:1544: thong thong snying rje'i bdag po ci de ltar byed dam zhes 'dzer zhing /
NK013(pa)001:1545: shin tu gdug pa'i sems kyis khros nas rngam mo //
NK013(pa)001:1546: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad zhabs brgyad du gnas nas /
NK013(pa)001:1547: rngam pa'i skad kyis thugs rjes 'dul ba'i thabs kyis shin tu khros nas /
NK013(pa)001:1550: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK013(pa)001:1552: dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa /
NK013(pa)001:1553: gdug pa chen po'i tshogs de dag gi snying dang dbang po kun phyung /
NK013(pa)001:1555: yan lag kun bcad gtubs nas sha kun zos /
NK013(pa)001:1558: de nas h+aum h+aum h+aum b+h+yo e a ra li dzahdzah zhes brjod pas /
NK013(pa)001:1559: phyos bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams nam mkha' dang bcas
NK013(pa)001:1560: pa yungs 'bru gcig tsam du chud par bsdus so
NK013(pa)001:1561: // de nas 'byung po ma lus pa'i rgyal po'i
NK013(pa)001:1562: yang rgyal po dregs pa chen po la sogs pa'i
NK013(pa)001:1563: chung ma 'byung po thams cad kyi rje mo'i yang
NK013(pa)001:1564: // rje mo / srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK013(pa)001:1577: ra ro khrag 'thung myos ma dang /
NK013(pa)001:1589: ra mgo dmar ser chen mo dang /
NK013(pa)001:1590: bum sna sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK013(pa)001:1591: gsus 'dzin ser nag chen mo la sogs pa /
NK013(pa)001:1593: g.yog dang yang g.yog 'khor zhing gi rdul snyed kyang bsdus so //
NK013(pa)001:1594: de nas bcom lda 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung chen pos 'dul ba'i thabs kyis /
NK013(pa)001:1595: yang rigs lnga'i 'jigs byed chen por snang bar byas nas /
NK013(pa)001:1596: de dag kun kyang dgyes pas rol pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK013(pa)001:1597: gyi sprin 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK013(pa)001:1598: la snyoms par zhugs te sku dang gsung dang thugs
NK013(pa)001:1600: +aahh+aum badz+ra pra be sha a la la hoh zhes brjod pas /
NK013(pa)001:1601: 'byung mo'i rgyal mo rnams shin tu chags pa'i yid g.yos nas /
NK013(pa)001:1602: pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor sdud cing rgyas par gyur nas /
NK013(pa)001:1603: dper na khab len la lcags 'du ba'i tshul du /
NK013(pa)001:1604: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung chen po rdo rje'i sku la /
NK013(pa)001:1605: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK013(pa)001:1612: ser nag chen mo rnams 'khril lo //
NK013(pa)001:1613: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK013(pa)001:1619: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po rin po che'i sku la /
NK013(pa)001:1625: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po pad+ma'i sku la /
NK013(pa)001:1631: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po kun tu las kyi sku la /
NK013(pa)001:1637: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag gis /
NK013(pa)001:1639: pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs bsdus nas shin tu bcum par gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:1640: de nas dgyes te ha zhes brjod pas /
NK013(pa)001:1641: byang chub sems kyi sprin las /
NK013(pa)001:1648: sme sha can gyi tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1649: ma tshogs ma'i tshogs rnams rang rang gi lag cha dang /
NK013(pa)001:1650: ngo mtshar dang bcas nas 'thon to /
NK013(pa)001:1652: / 'thon nas kyang 'bar ba chen po 'khor lo'i rtsibs
NK013(pa)001:1653: mchan shar phyogs nas 'khor bar 'jigs pa'i gzugs rang
NK013(pa)001:1654: gi lag cha dang bcas nas 'khod do //
NK013(pa)001:1655: de nas shin tu dgyes nas he zhes brjod pas /
NK013(pa)001:1656: seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1657: stag gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1658: wa gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1659: khyi gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1660: bzhad gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1661: kang ka'i gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1662: khwa gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1663: 'ug pa'i gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams /
NK013(pa)001:1664: rang rang gi lag cha dang ngo mtshar dang bcas nas 'thon par gyur to /
NK013(pa)001:1666: / 'thon nas kyang 'bar ba chen po'i 'khor lo'i phyi
NK013(pa)001:1667: rol shar phyogs nas 'khor bar rngam pa'i mdangs kyi
NK013(pa)001:1668: 'khod do // de nas shin tu dgyes pas phyogs
NK013(pa)001:1669: bcu'i zhing ma lus par khyab nas phata ces brjod
NK013(pa)001:1670: 'khod do // pas / rdo rje sring 'gro ma'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1671: rdo rje gdong mo'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1672: rdo rje 'jig rten ma'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1673: rdo rje ro langs ma'i tshogs rnams rang rang gi lag cha dang /
NK013(pa)001:1674: ngo mtshar du ma bcas nas 'thon par gyur to /
NK013(pa)001:1676: / 'thon nas kyang 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgor shin tu rngam pa'i gzugs kyis gnas so //
NK013(pa)001:1677: de nas dgyes pa chen po'i sprin las phyogs bcu nas phata ces bsgrags pas /
NK013(pa)001:1678: thams cad khros nas ma mo thams cad kyang rang
NK013(pa)001:1679: rang gi gnas ga la ba der yud tsam gyis
NK013(pa)001:1680: phyin par bakye'o // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes
NK013(pa)001:1681: pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung chen po de dag
NK013(pa)001:1682: kun thugs rje chen po bdud rtsi 'byung ba zhes
NK013(pa)001:1683: bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas
NK013(pa)001:1684: phyin par bakye'o // / sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK013(pa)001:1685: badz+ra ma h+aa a mri ta ma h+aa kro d+ha am am am zhes brjod pas /
NK013(pa)001:1686: dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa thams cad /
NK013(pa)001:1687: bcom ldan 'das khro bo chen po de dag gis bsnams nas bton te /
NK013(pa)001:1688: mi gtsang ba'i 'dam gyi rgya mtshor chud pa las
NK013(pa)001:1689: bsnams nas u tsush+ma kro d+ha phyung nas 'dam kun
NK013(pa)001:1690: 'thungs te dran pa slar rnyed nas /
NK013(pa)001:1691: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs de dag thams cad kyang dbu dgu brgya phyag stong brgyad brgya /
NK013(pa)001:1693: sku 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor na bzhugs par mthong ngo //
NK013(pa)001:1694: de'i dus su 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i srid
NK013(pa)001:1695: pa kun tu dregs pa'i dbang phyug thams cad 'dul
NK013(pa)001:1696: ba'i thabs sna tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab par so
NK013(pa)001:1697: sor snang bas dus gcig tu btul lo //
NK013(pa)001:1698: de nas de dag shin tu 'dar zhing bred pa rab tu zhum pa'i nga ros /
NK013(pa)001:1701: 'bangs su nan tan ma bgyis na //
NK013(pa)001:1702: mgo dang lus ni brgyar 'gas shing //
NK013(pa)001:1703: snying yang 'gas shing gtub gyur cig /
NK013(pa)001:1704: rul myags 'tshig nas brlag pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:1705: dmyal bar lhung nas 'bod par shog /
NK013(pa)001:1706: ces 'bangs su mchi bar mna' bor nas /
NK013(pa)001:1707: dkyil 'khor gyi gdan du bzhag go //
NK013(pa)001:1708: thams cad kyis mgrin gcig tu yang smras pa /
NK013(pa)001:1709: bdag cag rnams kyi mchis brang dang //
