NK013(pa)001:1710: ma dang bu mo sring mo rnams //
NK013(pa)001:1711: dkyil 'khor chen por bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)001:1712: dpa' bo lha rjes bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)001:1713: bdag cag so so 'khor bcas kyi //
NK013(pa)001:1715: ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa yang //
NK013(pa)001:1716: gtsug gi nor bu 'bar ba ltar //
NK013(pa)001:1717: g.yo sgyu med cing gus ldan pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:1718: sems kyis blangs nas spyi bo yi //
NK013(pa)001:1719: gtsug tu bzhag ste bkur bar bgyi //
NK013(pa)001:1720: de yi dgos pa ci yang rung //
NK013(pa)001:1721: ma lus rdzogs par bdag cag bsgrub //
NK013(pa)001:1722: gal te dpa' bo'i spyan snga 'dir //
NK013(pa)001:1723: smras pa bzhin du ma bsgrubs na //
NK013(pa)001:1724: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo lus snying //
NK013(pa)001:1725: bkas gtubs dum bur rul bar mchi'o //
NK013(pa)001:1727: de nas de dag gi chung ma'i tshogs dang /
NK013(pa)001:1729: bu mo'i tshogs thams cad dkyil 'khor du yud tsam gyis 'ongs nas /
NK013(pa)001:1730: thams cad kyis mgrin gcig tu smras pa /
NK013(pa)001:1731: bdag cag 'khor tshogs thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)001:1732: dpa' bo chen po'i 'bangs su mchi //
NK013(pa)001:1733: dpa' bo chen pos bdag cag la //
NK013(pa)001:1734: las kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK013(pa)001:1736: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos lag
NK013(pa)001:1737: tu rdo rje byin nas ming gi dbang bskur te
NK013(pa)001:1738: dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol du bkod do //
NK013(pa)001:1739: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:1740: las khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi sprin
NK013(pa)001:1741: rnam par spros pa'i le'u ste bco lnga pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:1743: // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos dkyil
NK013(pa)001:1744: 'khor gyi tshogs chen po 'di dag dam tshig gis
NK013(pa)001:1746: de bzhin gshegs pa khro bo khrag 'thung chen po
NK013(pa)001:1747: btsun mo dang bcas pa'i tshogs de dag gi sku
NK013(pa)001:1748: dang gsung thugs rdo rje ye shes rngam pa las
NK013(pa)001:1749: gsung gi dkyil 'khor 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK013(pa)001:1750: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK013(pa)001:1751: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba du sh+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:1752: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK013(pa)001:1753: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK013(pa)001:1754: h+aum h+aum phata / rat+na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru
NK013(pa)001:1755: ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba du sh+tan+ta ka ha na
NK013(pa)001:1756: da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:1757: pad+ma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK013(pa)001:1758: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u
NK013(pa)001:1759: h'u h'u phata / karma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru
NK013(pa)001:1760: ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da
NK013(pa)001:1761: ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum hum phata /
NK013(pa)001:1762: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai sarba dush+tana h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:1763: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:1764: ma h+aa s+aur+ya rat+na ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai bi da ma h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:1765: 'di sam skri ta dang bstun na cung zad the
NK013(pa)001:1766: tshom du snang yang rgyud las sam skri ta kho
NK013(pa)001:1767: na'i nges pa med pas rong zom gyi gsung bzhin
NK013(pa)001:1768: bcos nas rgod mar bsgyur ba'o //
NK013(pa)001:1769: h+r+ai sh+rut+ta sa man+ta pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai kh+aa hi h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:1770: sarba a mo g+ha ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai bi shwa h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)001:1780: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai he /
NK013(pa)001:1782: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK013(pa)001:1783: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kh+ai he /
NK013(pa)001:1785: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+ai he /
NK013(pa)001:1786: badz+ra +au lu ka mu kh+ai he /

NK013(pa)001:1790: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK013(pa)001:1791: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK013(pa)001:1797: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK013(pa)001:1798: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)001:1799: thugs rje khro dpal rngam pa'i tshogs /
NK013(pa)001:1801: / 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK013(pa)001:1802: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK013(pa)001:1803: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)001:1804: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya phata /
NK013(pa)001:1805: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya hoh a li u
NK013(pa)001:1806: li t+aa li ta p+aa li damsh+t+aa go n+aa roo
NK013(pa)001:1807: dri / kham ram yo gi n+ai kh+aa hi hoh
NK013(pa)001:1808: glu 'di zur chag gi skad yin par rong zom
NK013(pa)001:1809: chos bzang bzhed ces lo chen bsod nams rgya mtsho
NK013(pa)001:1810: dri / gsung / h+aum ha he phata /
NK013(pa)001:1812: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad tshig /
NK013(pa)001:1819: thams cad du 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs kyis gang /
NK013(pa)001:1821: kun tu gang bar gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:1822: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:1823: las khro bo'i tshogs chen po'i gsung gi dkyil 'khor
NK013(pa)001:1824: spros pa'i le'u ste bcu drug pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:1826: // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos /
NK013(pa)001:1827: de dag gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do /
NK013(pa)001:1830: gru chad bzhis ni rnam par brgyan //
NK013(pa)001:1831: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan /
NK013(pa)001:1833: / 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes //
NK013(pa)001:1834: thod sprul sna tshogs nyi mas brjid /
NK013(pa)001:1837: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK013(pa)001:1838: gtum pa dom gyi sbar bas ni //
NK013(pa)001:1839: dbang phyug lha chen la sogs bzung //
NK013(pa)001:1840: smug nag sngo nag ser nag dang //
NK013(pa)001:1841: dmar nag ljang nag 'jigs pa'i sku //
NK013(pa)001:1842: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK013(pa)001:1843: ko rlon gos ni sna tshogs gyon //
NK013(pa)001:1844: rngam pa'i sgra chen 'jigs par sgrogs //
NK013(pa)001:1845: sbrul dang thod phreng nyi zla'i chas //
NK013(pa)001:1846: stong gi 'jig rten khor yug bcas //
NK013(pa)001:1847: rdo rje dung chen gang ba dang //
NK013(pa)001:1848: ral gri dgra s+t+wa gshol la sogs //
NK013(pa)001:1849: rang gi lag cha sna tshogs te //
NK013(pa)001:1851: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya dang //
NK013(pa)001:1852: sgo bzhi'i phyag rgyas rab mdzes shing //
NK013(pa)001:1853: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)001:1854: bcu gnyis dang ni brgyad kyis mdzes //
NK013(pa)001:1855: rang gi stan dang lag cha dang //
NK013(pa)001:1856: ci bgyi zhes ni chas te gnas //
NK013(pa)001:1858: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad du 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal bar gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:1859: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:1860: las khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu
NK013(pa)001:1862: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po'i mnyes
NK013(pa)001:1863: pa'i mchod pa chen po 'di ched du brjod do
NK013(pa)001:1864: // de la mchod sbyin dam pa ni //
NK013(pa)001:1865: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK013(pa)001:1866: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK013(pa)001:1867: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK013(pa)001:1868: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya'o /
NK013(pa)001:1870: / 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)001:1871: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya //
NK013(pa)001:1872: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen po dag /
NK013(pa)001:1873: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la dbul //
NK013(pa)001:1874: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK013(pa)001:1875: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK013(pa)001:1877: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK013(pa)001:1878: bde gshegs yon tan rmad po che //
NK013(pa)001:1879: gzhan nas yod 'ongs ma yin te //
NK013(pa)001:1880: lha srin la sogs smos ci dgos //
NK013(pa)001:1881: rnal 'byor las su rung rnams kyis //
NK013(pa)001:1882: phyag rgya chen po rdzogs 'gyur zhing //
NK013(pa)001:1883: gsal la yid gnyis med pas na //
NK013(pa)001:1886: mnyes pa'i mchod pa chen pos 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad khyab par gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:1887: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:1888: las mchod sbyin dam pa bstan pa'i le'u ste bco
NK013(pa)001:1890: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos sngags
NK013(pa)001:1891: 'chang rnams don yod par bya ba'i phyir dam tshig
NK013(pa)001:1892: chen po 'di ched du brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:1893: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK013(pa)001:1894: nyon mongs las rnams kun spyod kyang //
NK013(pa)001:1895: byas la mi sogs tshogs 'gyur te //
NK013(pa)001:1896: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK013(pa)001:1897: bla med mchog gi dam tshig tu /
NK013(pa)001:1899: / 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshul khrim dang //
NK013(pa)001:1900: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK013(pa)001:1901: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK013(pa)001:1902: yod med dbu ma'ang mi dmigs shing //
NK013(pa)001:1903: sgyu ma mig yor lta bu'i tshul //
NK013(pa)001:1904: srog med srog kyang gcad du med //
NK013(pa)001:1905: srog dang skyes bu log rtog tsam //
NK013(pa)001:1906: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med pas /
NK013(pa)001:1908: / 'phrul dag'i tshul te tha dad min //
NK013(pa)001:1909: gzhan dang ma byin med pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)001:1910: blangs med thams cad nyid kyi dbyings //
NK013(pa)001:1911: chos rnams sgyu ma lta bu la //
NK013(pa)001:1912: ming dang tshig tu btags pa rdzun //
NK013(pa)001:1913: rdzun nyid la ni brdzun spyod pa //
NK013(pa)001:1914: rdzun zhes btags tsam yod ma yin //
NK013(pa)001:1915: ma chags pa la chags pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:1916: chags pa nyid na chags pa med //
NK013(pa)001:1917: de ni tshangs mchog rgyal po ste //
NK013(pa)001:1918: shin tu chags pa chen po yin //
NK013(pa)001:1919: bla med mi spangs bla ma bkur //
NK013(pa)001:1920: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK013(pa)001:1921: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK013(pa)001:1922: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya /
NK013(pa)001:1924: / 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams te //
NK013(pa)001:1925: bsgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1926: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK013(pa)001:1927: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK013(pa)001:1928: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK013(pa)001:1929: dag pa'i snod chu mi dor ro //
NK013(pa)001:1930: yan lag bcu yi dam tshig ste //
NK013(pa)001:1931: ye nas dag mnyam rtogs pas spyad //
NK013(pa)001:1932: bsrung zhing bsgrub pa'i dam tshig lnga //
NK013(pa)001:1933: rtsa ba yin te rigs med 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:1934: mi spang mi dor lnga gnyis ni //
NK013(pa)001:1936: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yi //
NK013(pa)001:1937: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK013(pa)001:1938: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob 'gyur bas /
NK013(pa)001:1940: / 'das na sangs rgyas ma yin no //
NK013(pa)001:1941: rtsa ba nyams pa'i 'chal ba dag /
NK013(pa)001:1942: gso la nye bar mi brtson dang //
NK013(pa)001:1943: skad cig yud tsam smra ma byed //
NK013(pa)001:1944: nyams gyur nyes pa brjod mi lang //
NK013(pa)001:1945: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK013(pa)001:1946: sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:1947: yid du mi 'ong sna tshogs pa'i /
NK013(pa)001:1950: yan lag dam tshig nyams gyur na /
NK013(pa)001:1952: / 'bras bu med cing ngan song ltung //
NK013(pa)001:1953: dam tshig rnams ni rdo rje che //
NK013(pa)001:1954: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin //
NK013(pa)001:1955: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni //
NK013(pa)001:1956: gcig la'ang gnyis dang bcu phrag gsum /
NK013(pa)001:1957: yan lag dam tshig lnga gnyis la //
NK013(pa)001:1958: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su dbye //
NK013(pa)001:1959: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che /
NK013(pa)001:1961: / 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK013(pa)001:1962: srid gsum 'gro ba ji snyed pa //
NK013(pa)001:1963: rtog 'dul dam tshig de snyed spros //
NK013(pa)001:1964: gzhan yang rgyal mchog kun bzang gi //
NK013(pa)001:1965: thams cad ma lus phyag rgya yis //
NK013(pa)001:1966: sgrub med mchog dam ma lus 'grub //
NK013(pa)001:1967: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1968: rgyal ba'i rigs mchog 'dzin pa de /
NK013(pa)001:1971: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK013(pa)001:1972: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis rlob //
NK013(pa)001:1973: bde gshegs nyid kyi yul la zhugs /
NK013(pa)001:1975: / 'jig med kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK013(pa)001:1976: ji bzhin nyid dang 'dul ba'i thabs //
NK013(pa)001:1977: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas 'dus //
NK013(pa)001:1978: ma lus rnam dag lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)001:1979: nyams na bskangs pas rdzogs pa dang //
NK013(pa)001:1980: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1982: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la 'dul bar gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:1983: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las dam tshig gi le'u ste bcu dgu pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:1985: // dens de bzhin gshegs pa bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa
NK013(pa)001:1986: chen po lhun gyis grub pa'i dam tshig byin gyis
NK013(pa)001:1987: rlob pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms
NK013(pa)001:1988: par zhugs nas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do
NK013(pa)001:1989: // e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1990: 'bar ba gtum chen rngam pa la //
NK013(pa)001:1991: khros pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK013(pa)001:1992: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK013(pa)001:1993: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la /
NK013(pa)001:1994: mtshan ma ming du bcas par bya //
NK013(pa)001:1995: bkug nas rdo rje phur bus gdab //
NK013(pa)001:1996: rdul du byas la tshogs la dbul //
NK013(pa)001:1997: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK013(pa)001:1998: lu gu rgyud du sprel bsdams nas //
NK013(pa)001:1999: bcings gyur bskyod nas phyogs bcur g.yos //
NK013(pa)001:2001: bam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK013(pa)001:2002: 'bar ba gzi brjid lhun chen la //
NK013(pa)001:2003: chags pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK013(pa)001:2004: rdo rje gsung yang dbang du 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:2005: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK013(pa)001:2006: mtshan ma ming du bcas par bya //
NK013(pa)001:2007: rdo rje chags pa'i phur pas gdab //
NK013(pa)001:2008: chags pa'i tshogs la thim par dbul //
NK013(pa)001:2009: bam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK013(pa)001:2010: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams nas /
NK013(pa)001:2014: ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK013(pa)001:2016: dga' ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK013(pa)001:2017: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK013(pa)001:2018: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK013(pa)001:2019: yon tan yid bzhin gter du brtag /
NK013(pa)001:2020: nga rgyal dga' 'phro'i phur pas gdab //
NK013(pa)001:2021: rdo rjee gzi chen 'phel bar dbul //
NK013(pa)001:2022: ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK013(pa)001:2023: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams bskyod //
NK013(pa)001:2025: yid bzhin nam mkha' gang bar 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:2026: ya yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK013(pa)001:2027: gsal ba'i gzi brjid 'tsher ba la //
NK013(pa)001:2028: dang ba'i yid kyis mchog sbyin bya //
NK013(pa)001:2029: gtum chen rngam pa'ang lhan ner 'gyur //
NK013(pa)001:2030: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK013(pa)001:2031: gtum rngam 'khrug pa'i ngo bor brtag /
NK013(pa)001:2032: lhan ner gsal ba'i phur bus gdab /
NK013(pa)001:2034: / 'bar ba lhan ne'i tshogs la dbul //
NK013(pa)001:2035: ya yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK013(pa)001:2036: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams nas /
NK013(pa)001:2038: / 'bar ba lhan ne'i byin gyis khyab //
NK013(pa)001:2039: thams cad g.yo ba med par byed //
NK013(pa)001:2040: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)001:2041: lhag ma'i mchod sbyin 'dod pa sbyin //
NK013(pa)001:2042: rang gi dam tshig rab bsgrags nas //
NK013(pa)001:2043: gang 'dod las de byed par bsgo //
NK013(pa)001:2044: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru ka /
NK013(pa)001:2045: shin tu gdug cing gtum bag can //
NK013(pa)001:2046: thams cad ma lus 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:2047: dbang dang byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK013(pa)001:2048: lha chen la sogs dbang du bsdus /
NK013(pa)001:2050: / 'khor rnams dbang phyug slas su byas //
NK013(pa)001:2051: so so'i las rnams bskos pa de //
NK013(pa)001:2052: ji ltar dam bcas khas blangs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:2053: ma thogs myur du mngon par phyung //
NK013(pa)001:2054: dam bcas bzhin du ma byas na //
NK013(pa)001:2055: ji ltar dam bcas mna' bor ba'i //
NK013(pa)001:2057: dam tshig de las 'das gyur na //
NK013(pa)001:2058: mgo lus snying yang tshal pa bdun //
NK013(pa)001:2061: ji ltar bcol ba bzhin du byos //
NK013(pa)001:2062: las de mngon du ma byas na //
NK013(pa)001:2063: rang gis mna' bor khas blangs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:2065: rnal 'byor dam la gnas gyur pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:2066: las rnams yongs su bya ba dang /
NK013(pa)001:2068: / 'khor rnams bu gcig bzhin du skyong //
NK013(pa)001:2069: phra men ma yang dngos grub 'thob //
NK013(pa)001:2070: bcol ba'i las rnams mngon du byos //
NK013(pa)001:2072: khro bo sgrub pa'i las kyi gtso bo ni 'di yin no //
NK013(pa)001:2073: khrag 'thung chen po la sogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:2074: bro gar glu tshig chen pos ni //
NK013(pa)001:2075: thams cad thams cad ci 'dod pa //
NK013(pa)001:2076: thams cad thams cad byed pa yin //
NK013(pa)001:2077: mdzod ldan chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:2078: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni /
NK013(pa)001:2083: sbos mo chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:2084: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK013(pa)001:2085: lhan ner 'dod na lhan ner byed //
NK013(pa)001:2086: rmugs par 'dod na rmugs par byed //
NK013(pa)001:2087: seng gdong chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:2088: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK013(pa)001:2089: thams cad kun la za bar byed //
NK013(pa)001:2090: rdul tsha tsam yang med par byed //
NK013(pa)001:2091: bzhad gdong chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)001:2092: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK013(pa)001:2093: thams cad ma lus 'byin par byed //
NK013(pa)001:2094: kun la rab tu nyams par byed //
NK013(pa)001:2095: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)001:2096: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK013(pa)001:2097: rbad cing gtang bar bya ba ste //
NK013(pa)001:2098: thams cad thams cad byed pa yin //
NK013(pa)001:2099: ljon pa dang ni lcug phran tshal //
NK013(pa)001:2100: sdong gcig dang ni mes reg drung //
NK013(pa)001:2101: dang bas dga' bas chags pas dang //
NK013(pa)001:2102: khros pas k+aa li rab tu bya //
NK013(pa)001:2104: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la de bzhin gshegs pa nyid sbyong bar gyur to //
NK013(pa)001:2105: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:2106: las lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las byin gyis rlob
NK013(pa)001:2107: pa zhes bya ba'i le'u ste ni shu pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:2109: // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po'i tshogs
NK013(pa)001:2110: kyi dkyil 'khor gyis shin tu rngam pa'i mdangs kyis
NK013(pa)001:2112: h+aum gtum chen dus mtha'i me chen 'bar /
NK013(pa)001:2115: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK013(pa)001:2116: mche ba zangs yag za byed che hoh h+aum rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir //
NK013(pa)001:2117: gtum chen ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK013(pa)001:2118: a la ha la'i gad rgyangs che //
NK013(pa)001:2119: spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yeng ba che hoh h+aum khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK013(pa)001:2120: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal /
NK013(pa)001:2123: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che hoh h+aum khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po /
NK013(pa)001:2127: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che hoh h+aum bdud kun gyi ni bdag chen po //
NK013(pa)001:2128: bdud kyi bdud de bdud rnams 'joms /
NK013(pa)001:2132: / 'jigs byed chen po thig le che hoh h+aum rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK013(pa)001:2133: rdo rje chu bo sdud chen po //
NK013(pa)001:2134: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK013(pa)001:2135: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che hoh zhes ched du glu blangs so //
NK013(pa)001:2136: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK013(pa)001:2137: las khro bo la bstod pa'i le'u ste nyi shu
NK013(pa)001:2139: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos de
NK013(pa)001:2140: bzhin gshegs pa nyid la gsang sngags kyi rgyal po
NK013(pa)001:2141: brtan par gzung ba 'di ched du brjod do //
NK013(pa)001:2142: kye kye phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK013(pa)001:2143: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)001:2145: rnam rtog zhags pas so sor 'dzin //
NK013(pa)001:2146: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK013(pa)001:2147: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK013(pa)001:2148: ye shes ngo mtshar rab 'byams kyis //
NK013(pa)001:2149: don du mi 'gyur yongs ma gsungs //
NK013(pa)001:2150: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK013(pa)001:2151: phyag rgya gsang chen snying po 'di //
NK013(pa)001:2152: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK013(pa)001:2153: de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK013(pa)001:2154: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK013(pa)001:2155: gsang ba 'di las gzhan mi mnga' /
NK013(pa)001:2157: / sgro dang skur pa zhi ba yi //
NK013(pa)001:2158: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK013(pa)001:2159: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK013(pa)001:2160: de ni nges par lung bstan te //
NK013(pa)001:2161: sras ni thugs las skyes pa yin //
NK013(pa)001:2162: sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK013(pa)001:2164: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dbyer med par dgyes nas dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings /
NK013(pa)001:2165: sku gsung thugs lhun stug po bkod pa'i rgyan nyid du bzhugs so /
NK013(pa)001:2167: / 'phags pa rtog pa'i rgyal po sgyu 'phyul d+r+wa ba
NK013(pa)001:2168: le'u stong phrag brgya pa las mtshan nyid dang rgyud
NK013(pa)001:2169: thams cad kyi lung gi spyi de bzhin gshegs pa
NK013(pa)001:2170: thams cad kyi gsang ba gsang ba'i snying po de
NK013(pa)001:2171: kho na nyid nges pa las thams cad ma lus
NK013(pa)001:2172: par 'phros te 'khor lo bskor ba de dag gi
NK013(pa)001:2173: 'bras bu'i mchog / g.yung t+aika na rdzogs so zhes
NK013(pa)001:2174: pa re zhig rang rtsom zin pa la dgongs pa
NK013(pa)001:2175: 'bras bu'i mchog / 'dra'o // gsang ba'i snying po
NK013(pa)001:2176: de kho na nyid nges pa las mnyes pa dang
NK013(pa)001:2177: yongs su gzung ba'i le'u ste nyi shu gnyis pa'o
NK013(pa)001:2179: rgya gar gyi mkhan po bi ma la mi tra'i zhal snga nas dang /
NK013(pa)001:2180: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra dang /
NK013(pa)001:2181: rma +aa tsar+ya rin chen mchog gis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
NK013(pa)001:2182: spyir rtsa rgyud 'di la bod du lo pan bsdebs pa'i gzhi 'gyur gsum dang /
NK013(pa)001:2183: pan+di ta med pa'i rtsal 'gyur gnyis te 'gyur lnga byung bar grags pa las /
NK013(pa)001:2185: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba dang bee ro tsa na'i snga 'gyur /
NK013(pa)001:2186: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas dang gnyags dz+ny+aa na'i bar 'gyur /
NK013(pa)001:2187: bi ma la dang rma gnyags thun mong gi phyi 'gyur dang gsum las /
NK013(pa)001:2188: 'di ni phyi ma ste 'phyong can yin la /
NK013(pa)001:2189: snga ma gnyis la 'phyong med par grags so //
NK013(pa)001:2191: bstan pa phyi dar gyi tshe yongs rdzogs bstan pa'i
NK013(pa)001:2192: mnga' bdag thar lo nyi ma rgyal mtshan gyi 'gyur
NK013(pa)001:2193: dang / 'gos lo ts+aa ba gzhon nu dpal gyis 'gyur bcos mdzad pa gnyis su grags so //
